  "texts": [
    "With machines handling repetitive and mundane tasks, human workers can dedicate their time and energy to more complex and intellectually stimulating activities.",
    "This shift could enhance job satisfaction and promote personal and professional growth, as workers could acquire new skills and engage in higherlevel decision-making (Xu et al., 2021; Alves et al., 2023).",
    "Emphasis on human-machine collaboration and the continuous emergence and refinement of technology increases the need for adequate human-computer interaction (Brückner et al., 2023).",
    "One of the approaches to address this topic is using conversational AI to assist humans in manufacturing (Wellsandt et al., 2021).",
    "Training Large Language Models (LLMs) on numerous, diverse texts results in the embedding of extensive knowledge (Zhao et al., 2023)."
  ],
